            "category": "DHL Delivery",
            "tags": "speed,delivery times",
            "question": "How long do international DHL deliveries take?",
            "answer": "<p><strong>Most arrive in about 4–6 business days.</strong> Customs can add time in some countries. Your DHL tracking page shows the most up-to-date estimate.</p><p><a href=\"/pages/track-order\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Track your order</a></p>",
            "sources": ""
